{"baseRefName":"main","body":"Fixes #11\n\n## Summary\n\n- Stop the Pages download site from synthesizing direct `/releases/latest/download/...` links for assets that are absent from the latest release.\n- Resolve download buttons from GitHub Release API `browser_download_url` values and render missing macOS assets as unavailable non-links.\n- Extend browser e2e coverage so rendered links are compared with release metadata, using a local partial-release fixture and the live latest release for deployed checks.\n- Add post-upload Electron release validation for published asset metadata and HTTP `200` direct asset URLs.\n- Preserve the investigation, CI logs, issue screenshots, online references, and template comparison in `docs/case-studies/issue-11/`.\n\n## Root Cause\n\n`v0.9.5` exists and was published on 2026-05-10 at 12:49:05 UTC, but the release does not contain macOS DMG assets because the macOS signing/notarization secrets are not configured. The previous website still generated macOS direct asset URLs, and the previous Pages e2e checks only proved that the page loaded, not that the linked release assets existed.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `npm test`\n- `npm run check`\n- `npm run build:site`\n- `npm run test:pages:e2e -- --site-dir site/dist`\n- `git diff --check`\n\nNote: `npm run check` exits successfully and still reports the existing `src/bot/runner.js` complexity warning.\n\n## Reproduction Evidence\n\n- Before the fix, the new local browser e2e failed with: `Page links to release assets that are absent from the latest release: vk-bot-desktop-macos-arm64.dmg, vk-bot-desktop-macos-x64.dmg`.\n- The currently deployed live Pages site shows the same failure until this PR is deployed.\n- Direct latest checks for `v0.9.5` return `404` for both macOS DMGs and `200` for Linux, Windows, and `SHA256SUMS.txt`.\n\n## Screenshots\n\nDesktop after fix:\n\n![Desktop Pages download state](https://github.com/konard/vk-bot-desktop/blob/issue-11-5a698e976ba3/docs/screenshots/issue-11-pages-desktop.png?raw=true)\n\nMobile after fix:\n\n![Mobile Pages download state](https://github.com/konard/vk-bot-desktop/blob/issue-11-5a698e976ba3/docs/screenshots/issue-11-pages-mobile.png?raw=true)\n\n## Remaining Release Prerequisite\n\nmacOS downloads will stay unavailable until the repository is configured with `MAC_CSC_LINK`, `MAC_CSC_KEY_PASSWORD`, `APPLE_API_KEY`, `APPLE_API_KEY_ID`, and `APPLE_API_ISSUER`. This PR prevents broken installer links while keeping the signed macOS release policy intact.\n","files":[{"path":".changeset/issue-11-release-download-links.md","additions":5,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":".github/workflows/electron-release.yml","additions":37,"deletions":0,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":".github/workflows/pages.yml","additions":2,"deletions":0,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":".gitkeep","additions":2,"deletions":1,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":".jscpd.json","additions":3,"deletions":0,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":".lycheeignore","additions":0,"deletions":5,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":".prettierignore","additions":3,"deletions":0,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":"README.md","additions":6,"deletions":4,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":"docs/REQUIREMENTS.md","additions":12,"deletions":9,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-11/README.md","additions":170,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-11/artifacts/broken-release-link.png","additions":0,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-11/artifacts/build-site-after-favicon.log","additions":9,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-11/artifacts/build-site-after-fix.log","additions":9,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-11/artifacts/direct-latest-link-checks-v0.9.5.txt","additions":8,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-11/artifacts/electron-release-v0.9.4-run.json","additions":1,"dele